headline: Hilton Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date
summary: MCLEAN, Va., April 01, 2025--Hilton Worldwide Holdings Inc. (NYSE: HLT) will report first quarter 2025 financial results before the stock market opens on Tuesday, April 29, 2025, followed by a conference call at 9 a.m. EDT. Christopher J. Nassetta, president & chief executive officer, Hilton, and Kevin Jacobs, chief financial officer & president, global development, Hilton, will discuss the company's performance and lead a question-and-answer session.
